---
title: Creamy Seafood Pasta Bake with Roasted Broccoli
description: Super quick, no faff fishy pasta bake. Put your feet up when the bake is in the oven and expect many compliments around the dinner table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-seafood-pasta-bake-5e15be84-efca1842.jpg
